
<span class='GTTabs_titles'><b>Translation</b></span><br />
To live with you, not to be without you, is what I want<br />
Do you hear me?<br />
We can not live on the same world, but on separate paths<br />
Do you understand?<br />
It&#8217;s time for love, now, come now</p>
<p>It&#8217;s hard to be with you and without you<br />
Your absence is an ember in my heart<br />
Come with the rain<br />
Come with your sins if you want</p>
<p>Blow storms if you want<br />
Just smile and let roses flower in my life<br />
While I have been waiting<br />
Summer is over</p>
